questions.quote: Joey relax! My mother picked her up two hours ago. You were there!
Noo! My ex-boyfriend Richard! Y'know the tall guy, moustache?
No, I'm just gonna help him, you know, get 'de-Ursula-ized', like you know, like I did for Joey after he went out with her.
Although... it's also about the wedding... Ugh, alright... here. No... Oh God... Oh!
Oh, sure. Yeah, well, he was my high school boyfriend. Captain of the football team, really cute and he got a scholarship and went off to college.
There you go, that's the spirit! Okay! Now, if you need money, I will lend you money, but just get moving!
Oh! Oh, I can't believe it! I mean I think it's great! For him. She might be able to do better.
Oh, no umm, hi, that-that, you have to put that out, 'cause I'm pregnant.
Hey, I think Elizabeth is a little more serious than, "Spring break!" All right? I mean she's taken my class!
Really! God Ross, what were you thinking? I know it's really shallow, but a part of me wants him again.
